The effect of speaking a minority language at home on foreign
language learning
Jessica Tsimprea Malucha, *, Sebastian Kempertb, Marko Neumannc, Petra Stanata
a Institute for Educational Quality Improvement, Humboldt University, Unter den Linden 6, 10099 Berlin, Germany
